::Shadow Wing::

She was flying around enjoying the night sky.  She liked the evening time 
and enjoyed flying at night.  With her owl mode, it yearned to fly at night. 
  She spotted movement in the trees and used ehr telescopic vision.  She saw 
what looked like a wolf.  She flew downward and landed on a brach above the 
creature.
"Hello and how are you on this fine night? You look lost, need help in 
finding your way?"
